---
const postModules = import.meta.glob('./posts/*.{astro,md}', { eager: true });
const posts = Object.values(postModules)
  .map((mod) => mod.postMeta ?? mod.frontmatter)
  .filter(Boolean)
  .sort((a, b) => new Date(b.date).getTime() - new Date(a.date).getTime());
---
<html lang="zh-CN"><head><meta charset="utf-8" /><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" /><title>TWe1v3</title><meta name="description" content="能力沉淀、个人思考、自动化实验与安全研究。" /><style>:root{color-scheme:dark}body{margin:0;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",sans-serif;background:#0b1020;color:#e8ecf3}main{max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;padding:64px 24px}.tag{display:inline-block;margin-top:18px;padding:6px 10px;border:1px solid #2d3a57;border-radius:999px;color:#9cc0ff}h1{font-size:56px;margin:12px 0}.sub{font-size:20px;color:#aab6c8;max-width:700px;line-height:1.7}.grid{display:grid;gap:16px;margin-top:40px}.card{display:block;text-decoration:none;color:inherit;padding:20px;border:1px solid #25314a;border-radius:18px;background:#11182b}.card:hover{border-color:#4e75c9}.section-title{margin-top:52px;font-size:22px}.about{margin-top:20px;line-height:1.8;color:#c7d2e3}.date{color:#7f8da3;font-size:14px}.desc{margin:0;color:#c7d2e3}.meta{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px;margin-top:12px}.pill{padding:4px 8px;border:1px solid #2d3a57;border-radius:999px;color:#9cc0ff;font-size:12px}</style></head><body><main><div class="tag">Public layer · Astro · GitHub Pages</div><h1>TWe1v3</h1><p class="sub">这里是前台展示层。后台知识库继续沉淀，前台只放打磨后的内容：能力沉淀、个人思考、自动化实验与安全研究。</p><h2 class="section-title">最新内容</h2><div class="grid">{posts.map((post) => (<a class="card" href={post.href}><div class="date">{post.date}</div><h3>{post.title}</h3><p class="desc">{post.desc}</p>{post.tags?.length ? <div class="meta">{post.tags.map((tag) => <span class="pill">{tag}</span>)}</div> : null}</a>))}</div><h2 class="section-title">关于这个站</h2><div class="about"><p>这个站不会把所有原始草稿直接公开。更像一层筛选后的门面：把真正值得展示的研究、观点、流程和作品整理出来。</p><p>简单说，飞书和本地笔记负责沉淀，博客负责表达。</p></div></main></body></html>
